JOHANNESBURG – Controversy continues to dog suspended SARS boss Tom Moyane. The Sunday Times is reporting that he could be prosecuted for assault. READ: The Hawks investigating SARS commissioner Tom Moyane The teen mother of his 6-month-old grandson is accusing him of kicking her in the face. He’s allegedly accusing her of witchcraft and blames her for destroying his empire. Moyane faces an inquiry into his misconduct at the receiver of revenue. A date for the probe is yet to be announced. eNCA